[B]Mire Sirens v1.0.0[/B]
[I]Initial Release - Clean Fork[/I]

Mire Sirens is a community-maintained continuation of the Fen Light addon family, picking up after Fen Light AM was discontinued.

Changes from Fen Light AM v2.2.04:
- Rebranded to Mire Sirens by isleysharleen
- All shared API keys removed - users must supply their own
- Updater repointed to https://github.com/isleysharleen/isleysharleen.github.io
- Existing installs will be auto-detected and prompted to provide their own keys

You must register your own keys before metadata, lists, or Trakt sync will work:
- TMDb v3 API Key: https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
- TMDb v4 Read Access Token: same page, copy the "API Read Access Token" (starts with "eyJ")
- Trakt: https://trakt.tv/oauth/applications (redirect URI: urn:ietf:wg:oauth:2.0:oob)
